    <h2>What Defines Boutique Placement Agents</h2>
    <p>
      Boutique placement agents are specialized, often independent firms that provide personalized fundraising services distinct from bulge bracket placement agencies. These boutique placement agents typically focus on specific regions, asset classes, fund sizes, or investment strategies, offering deep expertise and tailored LP access within their areas of specialization.
    </p>

