        <li><strong>Nimble Execution:</strong> Faster decision-making and ability to adapt strategies mid-campaign without bureaucratic constraints</li>
        <li><strong>Selective LP Network:</strong> Curated relationships with 100-300 highly targeted institutional investors rather than broad databases</li>
        <li><strong>Aligned Economics:</strong> Often willing to structure creative fee arrangements including success-based pricing for emerging managers</li>
        <li><strong>Independent Advisory:</strong> Free from conflicts of interest associated with investment banking parents or proprietary fund interests</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>Why Choose Boutique Placement Agents</h3>
