        <li><strong>Specialized Strategies:</strong> Niche sectors (e.g., impact investing, sector-focused funds) where boutique expertise exceeds generalist knowledge</li>
        <li><strong>Regional Focus:</strong> Asia-Pacific or Latin American funds where boutique firms' local relationships provide superior access</li>
        <li><strong>Relationship-Driven:</strong> GPs prioritizing senior-level partnership and strategic counsel over transactional execution</li>
        <li><strong>Cost Sensitivity:</strong> Smaller funds seeking flexible fee structures that boutiques can more readily accommodate</li>
